<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:08:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>10月7日，12岁的马克在以色列度假。他独自一人回到家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-terrorists-killed-mom-and-her-boyfriend-i-ducked-and-i-ran/00000190-021a-dbe3-a1da-133f25fa0000</link><description>“恐怖分子杀死了妈妈和她的男朋友。我躲开并逃跑”：来自乌克兰的男孩静静地躺着，等待哈马斯的恐怖分子离开。体内中弹的他躲在斯德洛特一个陌生人的家里，直到第二天，一个陌生人主动提出帮助他</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-terrorists-killed-mom-and-her-boyfriend-i-ducked-and-i-ran/00000190-021a-dbe3-a1da-133f25fa0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在沙特阿拉伯的利益正受到以色列极右翼救世主部长的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</link><description>沙特与美国的防务协议将服务于以色列的安全理论和美国的战略，但它与内塔尼亚胡在政治上所信奉的救世主观点相冲突，使得以色列成为伊朗的合作伙伴，共同阻挠该协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 07:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员：尽管哈马斯“有效拒绝”拜登计划，加沙谈判仍在继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-despite-hamas-effective-rejection-of-biden-plan-hostage-talks-to-go-on/00000190-0e02-dfa9-a9fc-cfd7b04a0000</link><description>尽管哈马斯要求对以美框架进行重大改变，但以色列和外国消息人士表示，卡塔尔和埃及将继续与美国协调，看看能否达成协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-despite-hamas-effective-rejection-of-biden-plan-hostage-talks-to-go-on/00000190-0e02-dfa9-a9fc-cfd7b04a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称地面部队和战斗机瞄准拉法的哈马斯；哈马斯淡化加沙协议修正案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-live/hamas-urges-u-s-to-pressure-israel-in-effort-to-reach-ceasefire/00000190-0f3d-db28-a995-4fbd6d670000</link><description>哈马斯高级领导人表示，对加沙停火计划提出的修正案“并不重要” ■ 以色列国防军杀死黎巴嫩高级指挥官后，真主党向以色列北部发射了数百枚火箭弹 ■ 哈马斯表示，哈马斯要求以色列国防军在停火后第一周内全部撤出加沙第一阶段将归还人质尸体</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 01:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-live/hamas-urges-u-s-to-pressure-israel-in-effort-to-reach-ceasefire/00000190-0f3d-db28-a995-4fbd6d670000</guid></item><item><title>与伊朗挂钩，北方火箭弹袭击背后：被以色列杀害的真主党将军是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/tied-to-iran-behind-rocket-fire-on-north-who-was-the-hezbollah-general-killed-by-israel/00000190-0d68-db28-a995-4dfdbd230000</link><description>以色列军方表示，真主党高级指挥官塔勒布·萨米·阿卜杜拉是自 10 月敌对行动开始以来被杀的最高级别官员；以色列国防军还提到，他对真主党拥有重要的行动知识</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/tied-to-iran-behind-rocket-fire-on-north-who-was-the-hezbollah-general-killed-by-israel/00000190-0d68-db28-a995-4dfdbd230000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列和哈马斯不达成协议，加沙战斗将漫无目的地拖延，北部可能陷入全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</link><description>辛瓦尔的结束战争要求是内塔尼亚胡无意满足的，这让拜登政府不知所措 ■ 以色列在没有明确战略的情况下加大针对真主党高级领导人的打击力度，纳斯鲁拉则升级报复性袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，边境敌对行动达到顶峰时，真主党向以色列北部发射了 200 多枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</link><description>这次大规模袭击是在真主党在冲突中伤亡最高的人员被杀之后发生的。以色列国防军官员表示，以色列尚未决定对黎巴嫩进行大规模军事反应</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯要求以色列在休战一周内从加沙撤军，并首先释放人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/hamas-responds-to-egypt-qatar-on-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-release-plan/00000190-08db-d0f9-a1d5-d8fb2b450000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉《国土报》，此举“旨在确保以色列无法逃避协议的所有阶段，并在所有人质获释后重新投入战斗。”以色列称哈马斯的回应等于拒绝该提议本身</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/hamas-responds-to-egypt-qatar-on-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-release-plan/00000190-08db-d0f9-a1d5-d8fb2b450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 250 天：哈马斯提议修改美国支持的停火、人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-250-hamas-proposes-changes-to-u-s-backed-cease-fire-hostage-deal/00000190-0d51-dfa9-a9fc-cfd5d9ae0000</link><description>哈马斯对美国支持的加沙停火和释放人质协议提出多项修改 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了自战争开始以来被暗杀的真主党最高指挥官 ■ 真主党以大规模袭击回应，发射了 215 枚火箭弹 ■ 联合国新报告指责以色列和哈马斯战争罪行 ■ 以下是战争进入 250 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-250-hamas-proposes-changes-to-u-s-backed-cease-fire-hostage-deal/00000190-0d51-dfa9-a9fc-cfd5d9ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列告诉法庭，它扣留巴勒斯坦囚犯的尸体作为哈马斯交易的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-court-holding-palestinian-prisoners-body-as-bargaining-chip-for-hamas-deal/00000190-0cd8-d5ad-ad93-2cd9ff690000</link><description>瓦利德·达卡 (Walid Daqqa) 因参与 1986 年绑架和谋杀一名以色列国防军士兵而被定罪，于 4 月去世。该国承认这一决定标志着政策的转变，即不拒绝归还以色列平民恐怖分子的尸体以进行讨价还价</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:17:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-tells-court-holding-palestinian-prisoners-body-as-bargaining-chip-for-hamas-deal/00000190-0cd8-d5ad-ad93-2cd9ff690000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的联盟投票亵渎《托拉》</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-voted-to-desecrate-the-torah/00000190-0832-d0f9-a1d5-d83a5cd50000</link><description>执政联盟提出一项免除极端正统派男性征兵的法案，这在很多方面伤害了以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-voted-to-desecrate-the-torah/00000190-0832-d0f9-a1d5-d83a5cd50000</guid></item><item><title>《华尔街日报》：哈马斯绑架者将获救的人质锁在浴室里，威胁要杀死他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/wsj-hamas-captors-locked-rescued-hostages-in-bathroom-threatened-to-kill-them/00000190-0b96-dbe3-a1da-1bb7d7ef0000</link><description>《华尔街日报》称，有关周六获救的三名以色列人质被俘的新细节是基于对他们的亲属以及以色列安全和医疗官员的采访</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:35:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/wsj-hamas-captors-locked-rescued-hostages-in-bathroom-threatened-to-kill-them/00000190-0b96-dbe3-a1da-1bb7d7ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的空袭杀死了战争开始以来目标的“最高级”真主党指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/israeli-strike-in-lebanon-kills-most-senior-hezbollah-commander-targeted-since-war-began/00000190-0b56-db28-a995-4fdf34940000</link><description>三名真主党战士也在针对高级战地指挥官塔勒布·阿卜杜拉（又名阿布·塔勒布）的袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:00:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/israeli-strike-in-lebanon-kills-most-senior-hezbollah-commander-targeted-since-war-began/00000190-0b56-db28-a995-4fdf34940000</guid></item><item><title>联合国新报告指责以色列和哈马斯犯有反人类罪和战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/new-un-report-accuses-israel-and-hamas-of-crimes-against-humanity-and-war-crimes/00000190-0992-d067-adb0-8fb658b70000</link><description>以色列外交部发言人表示，该报告是来自“一个生来就有罪的实体”的“愤世嫉俗的政治戏剧”，该报告的领导人“都带有偏见，并受到明显的反以色列议程的玷污”</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/new-un-report-accuses-israel-and-hamas-of-crimes-against-humanity-and-war-crimes/00000190-0992-d067-adb0-8fb658b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军杀死黎巴嫩高级指挥官后，真主党向以色列北部发射了数百枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article-live/israeli-official-hamas-has-rejected-bidens-gaza-cease-fire-proposal/00000190-0a43-dd57-abb4-7a4b7dc20000</link><description>哈马斯要求以色列国防军在停火后第一周内全面撤出加沙，并表示将在第一阶段归还人质尸体 ■ 以色列国防军证实真主党高级指挥官塔勒布·阿卜杜拉在黎巴嫩被杀 ■ 真主党宣称对以色列北部大规模火箭弹袭击负责，誓言增加针对以色列的行动强度和数量 ■ 布林肯表示，哈马斯提出的停火修改建议中有些是可行的，有些则不可行</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 02:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article-live/israeli-official-hamas-has-rejected-bidens-gaza-cease-fire-proposal/00000190-0a43-dd57-abb4-7a4b7dc20000</guid></item><item><title>六名巴勒斯坦人在以色列针对西岸武装分子的反恐袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-counterterrorism-raid-against-west-bank-militants/00000190-09d5-d0f9-a1d5-d9fdbba60000</link><description>以色列军方一周内第二次使用攻击直升机瞄准巴勒斯坦武装人员使用的建筑物</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 00:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-counterterrorism-raid-against-west-bank-militants/00000190-09d5-d0f9-a1d5-d9fdbba60000</guid></item><item><title>尽管极右翼部长抗议，加沙被拘留者仍搬出“以色列的关塔那摩湾”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-protests-from-ben-gvir-gazan-detainees-moved-out-of-israels-guantanamo-bay/00000190-07b1-d067-adb0-8fb7d8750000</link><description>被拘留者正在被转移到其他以色列监狱或从斯德泰曼返回加沙地带，人权组织称那里的条件不人道，监禁可能构成战争罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 22:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-protests-from-ben-gvir-gazan-detainees-moved-out-of-israels-guantanamo-bay/00000190-07b1-d067-adb0-8fb7d8750000</guid></item><item><title>杰克·沙利文捍卫拜登在加沙战争期间对以色列的支持：坚决致力于以色列的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/sullivan-defends-bidens-support-for-israel-in-gaza-war-committed-to-israels-security/00000190-08ef-d067-adb0-8eef78a70000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问告诉美国犹太委员会，华盛顿和耶路撒冷之间的任何分歧都表明这两个盟友之间的密切关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 22:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/sullivan-defends-bidens-support-for-israel-in-gaza-war-committed-to-israels-security/00000190-08ef-d067-adb0-8eef78a70000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨退出内塔尼亚胡政府后，以色列民族团结党民意调查下滑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-unity-party-down-in-polls-after-gantz-quits-netanyahu-government/00000190-0675-d067-adb0-8e7712f30000</link><description>根据第 11、12 和 13 频道的调查，如果今天举行选举，本尼·甘茨领导的民族团结党将拥有 22-25 个席位，成为以色列最大政党。议会主要集团之间的平衡保持不变</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 19:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-unity-party-down-in-polls-after-gantz-quits-netanyahu-government/00000190-0675-d067-adb0-8e7712f30000</guid></item><item><title>在投票反对正统派草案豁免后，利库德集团议员呼吁解雇国防部长加兰特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/after-vote-against-haredi-draft-exemption-likud-lawmakers-call-to-fire-gallant/00000190-083b-d067-adb0-8e3fd2350000</link><description>该党消息人士称，活动人士对国防部长感到愤怒，他是唯一投票反对该法案的联盟成员。利库德集团党魁尼西姆·瓦图里和奥舍尔·什卡利姆呼吁内塔尼亚胡解雇他</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/after-vote-against-haredi-draft-exemption-likud-lawmakers-call-to-fire-gallant/00000190-083b-d067-adb0-8e3fd2350000</guid></item></channel></rss>